   attention in the business to business (B2B) market. The integration of
   the production planning functions and engineering design functions is an
   important area which has been addressed recently by some major
   enterprises.
   This paper proposes a methodology to support the integration of
   information flow between the applications of product data management
   (PDM) and manufacturing resource planning (MRP). A three-level structure
   including model development, model analysis, and system implementation
   was developed. An approach applying the concepts of semantic similarity
   to find the ``common{''} objects used in different business applications
